data.eml:eml: Selenops muehlmannorum spec. nov. from Southern Laos (Araneae: Selenopidae)

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Jäger, Peter, Praxaysombath, Bounthob (2011): Selenops muehlmannorum spec. nov. from Southern Laos (Araneae: Selenopidae). Zootaxa 2883: 65-68, URL: http://www.mapress.com/zootaxa/2011/f/zt02883p068.pdf
